# 📊 E-Commerce Sales Analytics Dashboard (SQL + Power BI)

## 📌 Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing an E-Commerce Sales dataset using SQL and Power BI to uncover business insights related to sales performance, customer behavior, product categories, payment methods, and regional trends. SQL was used for data preparation and transformation, while Power BI was used to build an interactive dashboard for visualization and decision-making.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

* Analyze overall sales performance.
* Identify top-performing products and categories.
* Understand customer purchasing behavior.
* Compare sales across countries and platforms.
* Evaluate payment methods and shipping preferences.
* Monitor monthly and quarterly sales trends.
* Build an interactive dashboard for business insights.

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies

* **SQL** – Data cleaning, table creation, transformation, and querying.
* **Power BI** – Dashboard development and interactive visualizations.
* **Power Query** – Data loading and preprocessing.
* **DAX** – Custom measures and KPIs.
* **Git & GitHub** – Version control and project hosting.

